  "Sunil Vaswani's Dubai-headquartered Stallion Group, named after his favorite animal, gets the bulk of its $4 billion in revenue from Africa. ",
  "Stallion's businesses span commodities trading, frozen foods, auto assembly and dealerships, including Nissan, Volkswagen, Audi and Porsche. ",
  "Vaswani is expanding Stallion's African footprint with a $9 billion investment in sectors such as steel, petrochemicals and agriculture. "
